      <p><a href="ch76s25.html#EpicMonsters(G-W)214">Thorciasids</a> speak Common, Elven, Dwarven, and <a href="ch66s06.html#MonstersG67">Giant</a>.</p>
      <p>A <a href="ch76s25.html#EpicMonsters(G-W)214">thorciasid's</a> natural weapons are treated as epic for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction.</p>
